headline: Teradyne Stock Gets RS Rating Lift
summary: Teradyne stock had its Relative Strength (RS) Rating upgraded from 68 to 79 Tuesday — a welcome improvement, but still shy of the 80 or better score you prefer to see. IBD's proprietary rating tracks market leadership with a 1 (worst) to 99 (best) score.
